{"tid":1917023,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"捲髮器討論 -  日本 Salonia 係香港用會唔會燒","createTime":"2020-03-09T08:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T14:15:16.000Z","uid":340766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"18011464a6590ed80c59410c680c172d6c4e4910","tid":1917023,"uid":340766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"自己每日都會捲頭髮 （就算home office 都係）<br />\n用左3年<br />\n買過2支唔係大牌子既捲髮器 around 250hkd<br />\n不過第一支就用用下自己燒左<br />\n第二支就個彈弓位斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次想試下大牌子會唔會可以用得耐d<br />\n有冇巴絲用過日本 Salonia <br />\n佢地d款好靚!! 仲要每季都有新限定色 <br />\n官網話係 &ldquo;國内海外兩用&rdquo; 但都驚會燒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左salonia 有咩好介紹 同埋香港邊度有得買"},{"pid":"588df2e5b14e181eec826631340af567d9de6d78","tid":1917023,"uid":347697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"唔使驚會燒啊 用咗好耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688e7fd3c266041ffac692da72de60af5fab6762","tid":1917023,"uid":84968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"買過佢兩次嘅直髮夾 <br />\n用得好好 不過好似有啲傷頭髮 就無再用了"},{"pid":"f06608ca6679afa7d98a1afa754b23df582febe3","tid":1917023,"uid":340766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"588df2e5b14e181eec826631340af567d9de6d78","tid":1917023,"uid":347697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"唔使驚會燒啊 用咗好耐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"佢兩用夾會唔會好難用 <br />\n平時用開卷 心思思想試下直髮夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db5e7515a50970b24c1c6fa493de7121639af3e","tid":1917023,"uid":340766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc